SMART PARKING SYSTEM 

SCENARIO 

You are a software engineer at a smart city development company. Your task is to design a Smart Parking System that keeps track of available and occupied parking spots in a shopping mall. The system should: 

Register cars entering and leaving the parking lot. 

Track available spots dynamically. 

Charge users based on parking duration. 

STEPS  

Use a dictionary to store parking slots ({slot_number: car_license_plate}). 

Implement functions to: 

Park a car (park_car(license_plate)) 

Remove a car when it leaves (remove_car(license_plate)) 

Calculate the total parking fee based on time spent. 

EXTRA CHALLENGES 

Implement VIP parking slots that charge premium. 

Add a feature to reserve spots in advance. 
